<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="duck-1-style.css">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@600&family=Bubblegum+Sans&family=Poppins:wght@300..700&family=Quicksand:wght@300..700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Mr. Know-It-All</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo-container">Logo</div>
        <nav class="navbar-container">
            <div class="nav-item">Home</div>
            <div class="nav-item">About Us</div>
            <div class="nav-item">Products</div>
            <div class="nav-item">Contact</div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <hr>

    <main class="product-page-container">
        <div class="product-details">
            <div class="product-image-section">
                <img class="product-image" src="assets/images/original/duck-university.jpg" alt="University Duck">
                <div class="alternate-images">
                    <img class="alternate-image" src="assets/images/original/duck-university 2.jpg" alt="University Duck Side View">
                    <img class="alternate-image" src="assets/images/original/duck-university 3.jpg" alt="University Duck Back View">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-info">
                <h1 class="product-title">Mr. Know-It-All</h1>
                <p class="product-description">
                    You know that one friend that always knows the answers? The one you always wanted by your side but you were afraid they would overshadow you? Look no further! This Desk Duck companion has all the look of a true know-it-all, but we promise he won't give you a single quack! Just tell him all about the work you're doing and watch him admire your progress like never before!
                </p>
                <p class="product-price">Price: $19.99</p>
                <button class="add-to-cart-btn">Add to Cart</button>
                <button class="buy-now-btn">Buy Now</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
